title: Dynamo 77 - And the Republic of Angels (2007) [V0]
description:
This is the second album by Dynamo 77 released in 2007. Feel free to share with your friends if you like it. For more information about records and tours, please visit www.dynamo77.com. Enjoy!


I didn't get a chance to say goodbye.
I didn't get a chance to say I love you.
Because I do, I miss you, my brother.

All songs written by J. Paulsson. This album was completed in September 2007. Copyright 2007 Unagi Produktion. Recorded at Unagi Produktion, Studio A. Vocals on 2, 5, 7 and 8 by Patricia Johansson and 3 by Josephine Johansson. Artwork by Johan Hjalmarsson and design by Olle Jonzon, www.interaktivamedier.se.
